    "name": "Shattered Sacrament",
    "prerequisite": "*Halcyon Speaker Dedication*; *Cascade Bearer's Spellcasting*",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "When Vigil fell to Tar-Baphon\u2019s Radiant Fire, that lost innocence brought you a deeper understanding of what faith means in the context of your own magic. When you cast a halcyon spell, you can choose for it to be a divine spell instead of arcane or primal. You gain a halcyon cantrip and a 1st-rank halcyon spell.",
